headline: Morgan Stanley Retains Hold on Progressive (PGR), Lowers PT on Softer Growth Estimates
summary: The Progressive Corp. (NYSE:PGR) is one of the best value stocks in Goldman Sachs’ portfolio. In a September 22 update, Morgan Stanley analyst Bob Huang marginally lowered the price target on the stock to $265 from $267, but maintained his Hold rating.
